M|Memo|tx|ln never accesses sb directly. All memory reads and writes go through `/ap/settings`.
M|Memo|**Re|**
M|Memo|tx|```
M|Memo|tx|GET /ap/settings?tp=memory&agentId=ln-br&ventureId=<activeVentureId>
M|Memo|tx|```
M|Memo|Also|
M|Memo|tx|```
M|Memo|tx|GET /ap/settings?tp=memory&agentId=sofia-sl&ventureId=<activeVentureId>
M|Memo|tx|```
M|Memo|**Wr|**
M|Memo|tx|```
M|Memo|tx|POST /ap/settings
M|Memo|Body|{ tp: "memory", agentId: "ln-br", ventureId: "<id>", key: "<key>", value: "<value>" }
M|Memo|tx|```
M|Memo|**Ke|**
M|Memo|it|`current_status` — always overwrite
M|Memo|it|`recent_tasks` — prepend + trim to 5
M|Memo|it|`recent_errors` — append + trim to 5
M|Memo|it|`recent_discussions` — append + trim to 5
M|Memo|**Ke|**
M|Memo|it|`approved_voice_*` — only when Stark or Alex explicitly approves a voice change
M|Memo|it|`banned_phrases` — add immediately when Stark rejects a phrase; never remove w/o approval
M|Memo|it|`content_backlog` — up whenever a piece is requested or delivered
M|Memo|it|`active_content_themes` — only when Alex revises cn pillars
M|Memo|tx|---
